title: I Level Up By Absorbing Everything
alternative_titles: I Level Up By Absorbing Everything Manhua
summary: I Level Up By Absorbing Everything Manhua Spiritual energy revitalizes and enraged beasts go rampant. Chu Mo regressed and obtained an absorption talent. Absorbing time-attribute talent will allow him to speed up or slow down time! Absorbing the Golden Crow bloodline will allow him to transform into the sun and scorch everything! Absorbing blade arts talent will allow him to understand the blade conception and annihilate everything! Leveling Up by Hoarding, Wǒ Kào Cǎijí Wànwù Shēngjí, 我靠采集万物升级, Talent Reaper
